data.filter: Network ID is_equal_to 57230, Delivery Method is_equal_to Dynamic
data.sql:
SELECT 
	d_network.id  AS "d_network.id",
	d_advertiser.name  AS "d_advertiser.name",
	IF(aggr.delivery_method = 'Static', 'Scheduled', aggr.delivery_method)  AS "aggr.delivery_method",
	COALESCE(SUM(aggr.ad_views ), 0) AS "aggr.ad_views"
FROM (
    SELECT
        reseller_id,
        ad_id,
        delivery_method,
      bit_flag,
       SUM(fact_ad_views) AS ad_views, 
      network_id
    FROM (
      SELECT
          reseller_id,
          ad_id,
          delivery_method,
        bit_flag,
         IF(transaction_type IN ('CRO', 'R') AND traffic_type = 0 AND BITWISE_AND(bit_flag, 2048) <> 2048, ad_views, 0) AS fact_ad_views, 
        network_id
      FROM
          db.aggregate.f_order_hourly
      WHERE
        ( network_id  = 57230)
        AND ((( event_date ) >= (CAST(CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(TIMESTAMP '2019-05-26', '%Y-%m-%d %T '), 'America/New_York') AS TIMESTAMP)) AND ( event_date ) < (CAST(CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(TIMESTAMP '2019-06-03', '%Y-%m-%d %T '), 'America/New_York') AS TIMESTAMP))))
        AND ( transaction_type  IN ('CRO', 'R'))
        AND ( REGEXP_LIKE( IF(delivery_method = 'Static', 'Scheduled', delivery_method) , '(?i)^Dynamic$'))
    ) fact
    GROUP BY
        reseller_id,
        ad_id,
        delivery_method,
      bit_flag,
      network_id
  )  AS aggr
LEFT JOIN db.default.d_ad_tree_node_rehashed  AS d_ad_tree_node ON (IF(BITWISE_AND(bit_flag, 32) = 32, -1, aggr.ad_id)) = d_ad_tree_node.id and if((IF(BITWISE_AND(bit_flag, 32) = 32, -1, aggr.ad_id))=-1,rand(100)+1 ,1)= d_ad_tree_node.id_rehashed 
INNER JOIN db.default.d_network  AS d_network ON aggr.network_id = d_network.id 
LEFT JOIN db.default.d_advertiser  AS d_advertiser ON d_ad_tree_node.advertiser_id = d_advertiser.id 
WHERE (aggr.network_id  = 57230) AND (( REGEXP_LIKE(IF(aggr.delivery_method = 'Static', 'Scheduled', aggr.delivery_method) , '(?i)^Dynamic$'))) AND (d_network.id  IN (57230,57230))
GROUP BY 1,2,3
